        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Distribution map of Aulacospira spp. in Thailand: 1 A. depressa 2 A. khaopratun 3 A. panhai 4 A. khaobote 5 A. lampangensis 6 A. smaesarnensis 7 A. pluangtong 8 Aulacospira tekavongae sp. nov. 9 Aulacospira nudtadhirai sp. nov. 10 Aulacospira vanwalleghemi sp. nov." , "Figure 4. A-D Aulacospira pluangtong (ZRCBUU 357) A shell B radula C, D genital system E-H Aulacospira nutadhirai sp. nov. E holotype (ZRCBUU 0391) F radula G, H genital system." , "Figure 5. A-D Aulacospira tekavongae sp. nov. A holotype (ZRCBU 0610) B radula C, D genital system E-H Aulacospira vanwalleghemi sp. nov. E holotype (ZRCBUU 732) F radula G, H genital system." ;
